    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This driver-focused example utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, ensuring direct tactile feedback. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh to ensure variable valve timing precision. The chassis retains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution, with the suspension benefiting from updated bushings to maintain sharp turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior displays minor road patina, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering a visceral, naturally aspirated performance profile.",
